Nun: (Sobbing) I signed the Cull Orders. I saw your names on the parchment and I didn't stop the ink. I thought the machine would bring peace... I didn't know it would just bring silence.
- "Heal my wounds."
    Nun: (Reaches out with trembling hands) I will take your agony. It is the only penance I have left.
